==Mandarin==
{{zh-hanzi-box|[[吗]]|嗎}}

===Pronunciation===
{{Pinyin-IPA|ma}}

===Particle===
{{cmn-particle|t|pin=ma|pint=ma|tra=嗎|sim=吗}}

# final interrogative particle on a yes/no question
#: 你喜欢'''嗎'''? nǐ xǐhuan ma?
#:: '''Do''' you like it?

====Usage notes====
The particule 嗎 allow to turn an affirmative sentence into a interogative sentence without modifying the sentence order.
:: 他喜欢? He like it.
:: 他喜欢'''嗎'''? '''Does''' he like it?

====See also====
* Question particle : [[呢]] ( reciprocal questions ).
* Question words : [[哪]] (what, which), [[谁]] (who).

